##### CI Jmeter #######

Install Jmeter on EC2 :
 : sudo apt install fontconfig openjdk-17-jre
 : wget https://downloads.apache.org/jmeter/binaries/apache-jmeter-5.6.2.tgz
 : tar -xzf apache-jmeter-5.6.2.tgz
 : sudo mv apache-jmeter-5.4.1 /opt/jmeter
 : sudo mv apache-jmeter-5.6.2 /opt/jmeter
 : echo 'export JMETER_HOME="/opt/jmeter"' >> ~/.bashrc
 : echo 'export PATH="$PATH:$JMETER_HOME/bin"' >> ~/.bashrc
 : source ~/.bashrc
 : jmeter --version

Install Jmeter Plugin in Jenkins

Plugin Name : Performance
